    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Styles and cultures of the easternmost extension of Africa including Somalia, Djibouti, Eritrea, and Ethiopia, that with East Africa (Kenya, Tanzania, and Uganda) make up Eastern Africa.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
